room_title: Escape room "The Timekeeper's Trapped!" by Escape Factor Chicago in Chicago
room_description: You've been summoned to the lab of the Official Interplanetary Timekeeper. An evil group has been bending time for their own benefit, placing your colleague in extreme peril. Using your unique blend of skills and teamwork, you and your guests must work together to free the Timekeeper. Can you complete your quest in time?
